What is Linux OS?
Linux Operating System has become popular in the market segments of desktops,servers and embedded devices.
Also, Linux is a good choice for host developer environment.

Why and How Course is designed?
This course is designed to meet the increased requirements of Linux as a developer host and target device environments.
This course aims at thorough understanding of Linux operating system with coverage on commands, OS internals, system programming & techniques to meet the requirements of emerging project technologies